              <span>•</span>
              <span>Free Tier Comparison</span>
              <span>•</span>
              <span>~10 min read</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              A generous free tier lets you prototype, benchmark, and production-test without upfront investment. This guide compares the free tier offerings of 26 active AI API providers, ranked by generosity, real-world usability, and whether you need a credit card to get started.
            </p>
          </header>

