            <p class="text-blue-800 text-sm">
              <strong>TL;DR:</strong> Groq offers the most generous free tier with 1,000 requests/day, no credit card required. Google Gemini 2.0 Flash is genuinely unlimited for free. Zhipu GLM-3-Turbo offers unlimited free calls for Chinese-language apps. FreeModel gives free credits with China-direct access, perfect for developers without proxy setup.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
            <h2>Introduction: Why Free Tiers Matter in 2026</h2>
            <p>As AI API costs continue to evolve, free tiers remain the single most important factor for developers evaluating new providers. A generous free tier lets you prototype, benchmark, and production-test without upfront investment. In 2026, the landscape ranges from genuinely unlimited free usage to modest signup credits — and the gap between the best and worst free offers is enormous.</p>
            <p>This guide compares the free tier offerings of <strong>26 active AI API providers</strong>, ranked by generosity, real-world usability, and whether you need a credit card to get started.</p>

            <h2>Tier 1: Truly Generous Free Tiers (No Credit Card, Real Usage)</h2>

            <h3>Groq — 1,000 Free Requests/Day</h3>
            <p>Groq stands out in 2026 with the industry most developer-friendly free tier: <strong>30 requests/minute, 14,400 tokens/minute, and up to 1,000 requests per day</strong> — all without requiring a credit card. Powered by their custom LPU inference engine, you get access to Llama 3.3 70B at blazing speeds (up to 1,250 tokens/sec on smaller models).</p>

            <h3>Google Gemini 2.0 Flash — Unlimited Free</h3>
            <p>Google offers unmatched generosity with <strong>Gemini 2.0 Flash free tier</strong>: unlimited API calls through their free quota. While rate limits apply for very high throughput, the free tier is genuinely usable for production prototyping. The 200K context window is included at no cost.</p>

            <h3>Zhipu GLM-3-Turbo — Free Model Calls</h3>
            <p>Zhipu AI offers <strong>GLM-3-Turbo with unlimited free API calls</strong>, making it one of the best options for Chinese developers who need consistent, no-cost access to a capable LLM.</p>

            <h2>Tier 2: Free Credits on Signup</h2>

            <h3>OpenAI — $5 Free Credits</h3>
            <p>OpenAI offers <strong>$5 in free API credits</strong> to new users. These credits expire after 3 months and cover GPT-4o mini and other models. A credit card is required.</p>

            <h3>DeepSeek — $2 Free Credits</h3>
            <p>DeepSeek provides <strong>$2 in free credits</strong> on signup — small but useful for testing. The key advantage is that DeepSeek pricing is already extremely low (¥1-8/1M tokens input), so $2 goes surprisingly far. No credit card required.</p>

            <h3>FreeModel — Free Credits + China Direct</h3>
            <p>FreeModel offers <strong>free credits on registration</strong> plus a critical advantage: <strong>direct access from China without a proxy</strong>, making it the best option for Chinese developers who want to test DeepSeek and other open-source models. <a href="https://freemodel.dev/invite/FRE-7a3b6220" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Sign up via FreeModel</a> to get started.</p>

            <h3>Fireworks AI — $5 Free Credits</h3>
            <p>Fireworks AI gives <strong>$5 in free credits</strong> for new accounts. Their high-throughput inference platform supports 80+ open-weight models with enterprise-grade SLAs.</p>

            <h3>Anyscale — $5 Free Credits</h3>
            <p>Anyscale provides <strong>$5 in free credits</strong> for new accounts, powered by the Ray distributed computing backend.</p>

            <h3>Block.AI (BAI) — $100 Free Credits (Limited Match)</h3>
            <p>Block.AI offers <strong>$100 in free credits</strong> through a limited-time 1:1 deposit match program.</p>

            <h3>Stability AI — 25 Free Credits</h3>
            <p>Stability AI offers <strong>25 free credits on signup</strong>, enough for 3-4 SD 3.5 Large images at 1024x1024.</p>

            <h2>Tier 3: Free Model Access (Rate Limited)</h2>

            <h3>OpenRouter — 50 Requests/Day + 25 Free Models</h3>
            <p>OpenRouter gives you <strong>50 free requests per day</strong> plus access to <strong>25 free models</strong> through a single API key.</p>

            <h3>Baidu ERNIE-Lite — Free Model</h3>
            <p>Baidu offers <strong>ERNIE-Lite for free</strong>, a capable Chinese-language model.</p>

            <h3>Alibaba Cloud — Free API Calls</h3>
            <p>Alibaba Cloud (Bailian) provides <strong>free API calls</strong> at limited quotas for their Qwen models.</p>

            <h3>ByteDance Doubao — Generous Free Quota</h3>
            <p>ByteDance offers a <strong>generous free quota for new users</strong> on the Doubao API.</p>

