              </tbody>
            </table>

            <h2>Conclusion</h2>
            <p>The 2026 AI API free tier landscape is remarkably generous. You can build, test, and even run production services entirely on free tiers from Groq, Google, Zhipu, and others. The decision tree is now:</p>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Need raw speed?</strong> Start with Groq free tier</li>
