            <p>If you are a Chinese developer looking for a reliable starting point with free credits and seamless access to DeepSeek and open-source models, <a href="https://freemodel.dev/invite/FRE-7a3b6220" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">sign up for FreeModel</a> to get started — no proxy, no credit card required.</p>
